  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à Ekiga</title>

    <para>
      <application>Ekiga</application> is a VoIP, IP Telephony, et Video Conferencing
      application that allows you to make audio et video calls to remote users with
      SIP or H.323 compatible hardware et software.  It supports many audio et video
      codecs et all modern VoIP features for both SIP et H.323.
      <application>Ekiga</application> is the first Open Source application to support
      both H.323 et SIP, as well as audio et video.
    </para>

    &lfs72_checked;

